{
  "stem": "1061.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the trains that were on that siding-- because, as you know, a factory like this must have a siding near it for transporting the-- the the goods to the factory and back-- that siding was used for the trains onto which this last camp was emptied onto those trains.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everybody that was not killed in the-- in the-- in the breakout the night before.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody who survived the horror of typhus, of starvation, of beating, of working to death in the factories.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After all the-- the hundreds of people who died, those of us who were left in the last camp were loaded onto a train.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was July 1944.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We did not know why we were being sent out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We did not know where we were being sent out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But after the war and of course reading history, we found out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I learned that the Russian offensive had started in the East.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Germans were now emptying all the camps, the so-called work camps-- which were slave labor camps-- that were in my area, where munition-- war-- the-- the-- The munitions factory that was full war production, the Germans did not feed you the piece of bread in the morning and that horrible soup in the evening because they loved you.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They kept you as long as they could because their war effort was based on the labor-- slave labor of these people in my hometown and the towns around.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when the Russians started coming west, all these camps were emptied-- being emptied.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And our camp went to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you see, when we arrived there at the end of July 1945-- or maybe August-- beginning of August, something like this-- there was only one crematorium working.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were unloaded.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had no idea where we were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were tattooed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Of course, we stood in line.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My sister Anna, the oldest one, got the first number.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My sister [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Kris, ?] got the second number, and I got the third number.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that whenever there will be reference to numbers, we would find ourselves in the same unit, you see.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were sent into the so-called sauna, which was-- which was a shower.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But they took away our clothes, and they just threw other clothes to us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the-- the thing that happened there, they were not-- at one time, I understand in Auschwitz, they would shave women's heads.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When our transport came, because now this was really the political situation and the-- the war was taking on another direction, they did not shave us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They just, you know, they sat you down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They took a pair of scissors, and they just chopped away some hair.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know how you would look like a-- you know, a horror, because this was long.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "This was short.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This was bald.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This-- whatever.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Little machines that people shave people's heads.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anyhow, my oldest sister had a friend-- my oldest sister Anna was always very tall.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she had a friend who was just as tall.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Irene is her name-- Irene Ross now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, anyhow, how-- however it was, my sister Anna was so incensed by the way we were treated.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They spat on us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The women, I think, were Czechoslovak attendant women.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They called us names.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They kicked us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They spit on us in that, move faster!",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this-- and sister, my oldest sister, said, you have no right to treat me like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Well, the-- her friend Irene said something similar.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Says, you shouldn't be treating people that this-- something like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Well, they were pulled back, sat down, and shaved to zero.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Well, I must tell you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In all the horror of the situation-- the anxiety, the fear, not knowing where we are and what is happening.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- and now where Father is, we didn't know either.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because Father was in the train with the men.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were with the women.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow, in all that, Anna and Irene burst out laughing because they looked absolutely-- well, there is no description, you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Grotesque is the closest, but it doesn't describe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These two, tall sticks of women with bald heads-- little-- little heads, you know, starved little faces, bald.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, of course, this was what they call in Polish, 'hangman's humor,' you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is the type of laughter that really should have been hysterics.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But anyhow, this was the women's section.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were processed through tattooing, through head-- the head being shaved, whatever being thrown some kind of clothes, whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, if you were a size 10, you got a size 52.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if you were a size 14, you got a size 6, whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
